    "body" : "<p>After adding dependencies open \"Gradle\" ('View'->Tool Windows->Gradle) tab and hit \"refresh\"</p>\n\n<p>example of adding (compile 'io.reactivex:rxjava:1.1.0'):</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/THZbq.png\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/THZbq.png\" alt=\"hit refresh\"></a></p>\n\n<p>If Idea still can not resolve dependency, hence it is possibly the dependency is not in mavenCentral() repository and you need add repository where this dependency located into repositories{}</p>\n"
